title: Cyal8erloser PK Vid III - Episode 666 - Runescape PK Video
description:
PKer: Cyal8erloser
PK Category: Initiate Pure (20 def)
Location: Edge based
Video: 3 Episode 666
Released: January 2007
Editor: Self Edited
Length: 15:05

Summary: This is Cyal8erloser\&#039;s final pk video. Its editing was excellent in light of its release date (early \&#039;07) and it is one of the strongest Initiate Pure videos ever released. It has tons of great loot, a great intro, great hits.... It shows Initiate Pures at their best, and displays their ability to just tear through their competition while risking nearly nothing. There are also clips in which Cya barrages in mystic, although the highlights are his melee kills. When I first saw this video, I decided that it had the best intro I had ever seen. I\&#039;ve since seen better, but this is still a very impressive and very relevant work. It spawned countless imitating followers who also used \&#039;Saw\&#039; theme music in their video introductions. The editing is done in a serious fashion, and displays many technical ideas that would be repeated again and again by the ensuing wave of impressionable fans.
